asing $\\mathbf{B}_{\\perp}$ forming a `time quasicrystal' which\noscillates in space and time for moderately strong drive.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Dec 2020 18:29:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Jan 2021 13:18:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 23 Mar 2021 11:38:30 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 27 May 2021 20:35:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-10"}
