 from light-curve modelling\nshows that Kumar's model does not provide reliable parameters. Finally,\nintrinsic pulsations of $\\beta$ Cep, SPB, $\\delta$ Sct, and $\\gamma$ Dor-type\nwere found in nine heartbeat systems. This opens an interesting possibility of\nstudies of pulsation-binarity interaction and the co-existence of forced and\nself-excited oscillations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Dec 2020 18:39:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Jan 2021 13:14:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-03"}
