 time reversal and inversion broken WSMs. The chiral anomaly\ninduced nonlinear planar effects predicted here along with the related\nparameter dependencies are hence possible to be realized in realistic WSMs in\nexperiment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Dec 2020 18:59:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 27 Mar 2022 14:56:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-29"}
