ation), and high PV\npenetration building areas make it a feasible approach. Over the studied week,\nthe strategy successfully controlled 100% of the violating power ramps, also\nobtaining a self-consumption ratio (SCR) of 59% and a grid-relief factor (GRF)\nof 61%.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Dec 2020 12:20:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 Mar 2021 09:33:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 30 Mar 2021 18:18:29 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 27 Jan 2022 16:33:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-28"}
