ainties in\nabundances of much less than 0.01~dex (2\\%). This agreement for simple atoms\ngives confidence in the FQ, LCAO and SE model approaches to be able to predict\nMN with the accuracy required for non-LTE modelling in stellar atmospheres.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Dec 2020 12:46:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-10"}
