 single carbon atoms, 2) sp-defect migration to\nsp$^2$-structure defects, 3) sp$^2$-defect annealing assisted by the sp atom\nand 4) subsequent annihilation of pairs of sp defects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Dec 2020 13:56:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-23"}
